# Node.js Task Management API

A backend API built with Node.js and Express for managing tasks. It provides endpoints for creating, reading, updating, and deleting tasks.

## Features
- RESTful API for task management.
- Includes CRUD functionality.
- Integrated with MongoDB for data persistence.
- Includes validation for API inputs.

## Prerequisites
- Node.js (v14 or later)
- MongoDB (Installed and running locally or on a remote server)
